fields.name: AddDefaultExtendedTimeRange
fields.description: Indicates if query time range should be extended with default time range of the query. Default value is false

fields.name: EndTime
fields.description: The end timeline date, so the results returned are before this date.

fields.name: InsightQueryIds
fields.description: List of Insights Query Id. If empty, default value is all insights of this entity

fields.name: StartTime
fields.description: The start timeline date, so the results returned are after this date.
